Elsevier Inc. All rights reserved.

DOI: 10.1016/j.sxmr.2015.10.005
PMID: 27872004 [Indexed for MEDLINE]


168. Clin Chem. 2017 Jan;63(1):66-72. doi: 10.1373/clinchem.2016.255075. Epub
