The emergence of longevous populations.

Colchero F(1)(2)(3), Rau R(3)(4), Jones OR(1)(5), Barthold JA(1)(6), Conde 
DA(1)(5), Lenart A(1)(6), Nemeth L(3), Scheuerlein A(3), Schoeley J(1)(3)(6), 
Torres C(1)(6), Zarulli V(1)(6), Altmann J(7)(8), Brockman DK(9), Bronikowski 
AM(10), Fedigan LM(11), Pusey AE(12), Stoinski TS(13), Strier KB(14), Baudisch 
A(1)(5)(6), Alberts SC(15)(12)(16)(17), Vaupel JW(18)(3)(6)(17).

Author information:
(1)Max-Planck Odense Center on the Biodemography of Aging, University of 
Southern Denmark, Odense 5230, Denmark.
(2)Department of Mathematics and Computer Science, University of Southern 
